uniPingServerSolutionV3.name: uniPingServerSolutionV3

revisions.description: npSmoke branch added, npRelHum branch extended
npRelayN, npRelayMode, npIoLineN, npRelHumSensorStatusH, npRelHumSensorStatus values changed
npCurLoop, npRelHumidity, npIr branches has added
Minor changes to IR module for IRC-TRv2
4 IO lines, Identification is changed from DKSF 52.4 to DKSF 52.5
npIoPulseCounter, npIoSinglePulseDuration, npIoSinglePulseStart is added Identification is changed from DKSF 52.3 to DKSF 52.4

uniPingServerSolutionV3.description: Generic MIB for NetPing remote sensing and control

npTrapEmailTo.name: npTrapEmailTo
npTrapEmailTo.description: user-specified e-mail for NetPing Trap Forwarding Service

npRelayMode.name: npRelayMode
npRelayMode.description: Control of relay: -1 - flip between on(1) and off(0) 0 - manual off 1 - manual on 2 - watchdog 3 - schedule 4 - both schedule and watchdog (while switched on by schedule) 5 - logic

npRelayStartReset.name: npRelayStartReset
npRelayStartReset.description: Write 1 to start reset (switch relay off for some time)

npRelayState.name: npRelayState
npRelayState.description: Actual relay state at the moment, regardless of source of control. 0 - relay is off 1 - relay is on

npThermoSensorN.name: npThermoSensorN
npThermoSensorN.description: The id of temperature sensor, 1 to 8

npThermoLow.name: npThermoLow
npThermoLow.description: Bottom margin of normal temperature range, deg.C

npThermoHigh.name: npThermoHigh
npThermoHigh.description: Top margin of normal temperature range, deg.C

npThermoTrapSensorN.name: npThermoTrapSensorN
npThermoTrapSensorN.description: The id of temperature sensor, 1 to 8

npThermoTrapLow.name: npThermoTrapLow
npThermoTrapLow.description: Bottom margin of normal temperature range, deg.C

npThermoTrapHigh.name: npThermoTrapHigh
npThermoTrapHigh.description: Top margin of normal temperature range, deg.C

npThermoTrap.name: npThermoTrap
npThermoTrap.description: Status of Thermo sensor is changed (crossing of normal temp. range)

npIoLineN.name: npIoLineN
npIoLineN.description: Number of IO line, from 1 to max supported

npIoLevelOut.name: npIoLevelOut
npIoLevelOut.description: Output level, 0 or 1. Write -1 to flip output.

npIoPulseCounter.name: npIoPulseCounter
npIoPulseCounter.description: Pulse Counter on IO input line (counts positive fronts) Write 0 to reset.

npIoSinglePulseDuration.name: npIoSinglePulseDuration
npIoSinglePulseDuration.description: Set duration of single pulse on IO output line, 100ms to 25500ms, min. step is 100ms

npIoSinglePulseStart.name: npIoSinglePulseStart
npIoSinglePulseStart.description: Write 1 to start single pulse on IO output. Output will be inverted for time, specified by npIoSinglePulseDuration

npIoTrapLineN.name: npIoTrapLineN
npIoTrapLineN.description: Trap data, Number of IO line

npIoTrapLevelIn.name: npIoTrapLevelIn
npIoTrapLevelIn.description: Trap data, new Input level, 0 or 1

npIoTrapLevelLegend.name: npIoTrapLevelLegend
npIoTrapLevelLegend.description: Legend for current logic level on the IO line

npIoTrap.name: npIoTrap
npIoTrap.description: Input state of IO line is changed

npCurLoopN.name: npCurLoopN
npCurLoopN.description: Index of current loop, 1 to max supported

npCurLoopV.name: npCurLoopV
npCurLoopV.description: Voltage drop on the loop, mV

npCurLoopPower.name: npCurLoopPower
npCurLoopPower.description: Control of loop power 0=Off, 1=On, 2=reset by off/on power

npCurLoopTrapN.name: npCurLoopTrapN
npCurLoopTrapN.description: Index of current loop, which status has changed

npCurLoopTrapV.name: npCurLoopTrapV
npCurLoopTrapV.description: Voltage drop on the loop, mV

npCurLoopTrap.name: npCurLoopTrap
npCurLoopTrap.description: Status of current loop N has changed!

npSmokeSensorN.name: npSmokeSensorN
npSmokeSensorN.description: The id of 1Wire Smoke sensor, 1 to 4

npSmokePower.name: npSmokePower
npSmokePower.description: Controls power on Smoke sensor current loop

npSmokeReset.name: npSmokeReset
npSmokeReset.description: Write 1 to switch off for approx. 10s to reset sensor

npSmokeTrapSensorN.name: npSmokeTrapSensorN
npSmokeTrapSensorN.description: The id of 1Wire Smoke sensor, 1 to 4

npSmokeTrap.name: npSmokeTrap
npSmokeTrap.description: Status of 1W Smoke sensor has changed

npRelHumN.name: npRelHumN
npRelHumN.description: Index of Humidity+Temperature sensor, 1 to max supported

npRelHumSafeRangeHigh.description: Relative Humidity safe range, top margin, %RH

npRelHumSafeRangeLow.description: Relative Humidity safe range, bottom margin, %RH

npRelHumTempSafeRangeHigh.description: Temperature safe range, top margin, deg.C

npRelHumTempSafeRangeLow.name: npRelHumTempSafeRangeLow

npRelHumTrapDataN.name: npRelHumTrapDataN

npRelHumTrapDataSafeRangeHigh.name: npRelHumTrapDataSafeRangeHigh
npRelHumTrapDataSafeRangeHigh.description: Relative Humidity safe range, top margin, %RH or deg.C

npRelHumTrapDataSafeRangeLow.name: npRelHumTrapDataSafeRangeLow
npRelHumTrapDataSafeRangeLow.description: Relative Humidity safe range, bottom margin, %RH or deg.C

npGsmRegistration.name: npGsmRegistration
npGsmRegistration.description: Status of modem registration in GSM network (AT+CREG? result)

npGsmStrength.name: npGsmStrength
npGsmStrength.description: GSM signal strength. 0..31 = 0..100%, 99 = unknown or n/a, 255 = updating info

npGsmSendSms.name: npGsmSendSms
npGsmSendSms.description: Send arbitrary SMS. Format: [phone_number,phone_number,...] Message One to four destination phone numbers If [] and numbers omitted, mesagge will be sent to preset numbers from SMS setup Cyrillic characters must be in UTF8 encoding.

npGsmTrap.name: npGsmTrap
npGsmTrap.description: GSM modem or SMS firmware problems

npIrPlayCmd.name: npIrPlayCmd
npIrPlayCmd.description: Write IR command number to send IR command

npIrReset.name: npIrReset
npIrReset.description: Write 1 to reset IR transiever. After reset, send IR command and check npIrStatus.

npSoftReboot.name: npSoftReboot
npSoftReboot.description: Write 1 to reboot device after current operations completition
